      "name": "Kobold Trap Squad",
      "sources": [
        {
          "link": {
            "alt": "Battlecry! pg. 184",
            "aonid": 268,
            "game-obj": "Sources",
            "name": "Battlecry! pg. 184",
            "type": "link"
          },
          "name": "Battlecry!",
          "page": 184,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "Kobold trap squads generally protect their warrens, but these groups sometimes range outside of their lairs at the behest of a powerful patron. Their goals are usually to scout a given location, but they can be tasked with procuring an item or resource for the good of the warren.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
